16
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:49,620
Os mais problemáticos
 são Randolph, Nobledilo,

17
00:04:49,620 --> 00:04:53,000
Diesel, o misterioso homem chaminé,

18
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,700
